{"tid":1802564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我哋要嘅係民主定第二個共産黨？","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T18:59:12.000Z","uid":176449,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"251e05cc154594074a092b9614977776d93ba5be","tid":1802564,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"要港獨嘅就會屌人淨係要五大訴求<br />\n又話人想繼續做共産黨隻狗<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求嗰班又話要遲啲先叫<br />\n唔好騎劫人<br />\n<br />\n幾時開始我哋分成咗兩派？<br />\n幾時開始我哋一定要大家有一模一樣嘅做法？<br />\n幾時開始我哋會迫其他人點諗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋一直以嚟都係同路人<br />\n為咗香港去爭取民主</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋不嬲都有人講話要港獨要歸英<br />\n每人都有自己嘅諗法 想要嘅結果<br />\n一直以嚟所有集會都有人做唔同嘅事<br />\n但我哋最終目的都係民主<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋迫其他人去做佢哋唔想嘅嘢<br />\n同共匪有咩分別??????<br />\n<br />\n1月1日<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣</span><span style=\"color: red;\">元旦</span><span style=\"color: green;\">遊行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要聽到所有人嘅聲音</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67398d1b94dfba4f63b1193658f4866f4a655ec5","tid":1802564,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一份未達標</span><br />\n而且差好遠呀<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 1xxxx/50000</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK99%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=379338ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"922f86f4eaf0a93527c795725a3aaefc592c5fc3","tid":1802564,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc